cast.overview: With the aid of a fellow Auschwitz survivor and a hand-written letter, an elderly man with dementia goes in search of the person responsible for the death of his family.
cast.title: Remember

details.biography:
James Cade is a Canadian actor. He is best known for playing Harmon Tedesco in the 2010 SpikeTV sitcom Blue Mountain State. He graduated from the National Theatre School of Canada and has since then performed in several theatre productions in Toronto, including Single Threat's production of A Quiet Place.
